{"tid":1119702,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"打麻雀教識你咩道理?","createTime":"2019-04-22T06:32:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-22T06:56:18.000Z","uid":186919,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"776d5ec2713a29d1b12c4db80b820c6e74d11447","tid":1119702,"uid":186919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T06:32:53.000Z","msg":"有一年新年同親戚開枱，副牌一棟起已經有7隻么牌，於是我就把心一橫試一次十三么。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n打到咁上下，出面三家都做萬子，自不然會搶萬子番子搶得好犀利。<br />\n<br />\n一路摸一路打，出面三家碰親啲番子我好多都喺佢地碰之前就摸到。有驚冇險出面三家都九章，我就摸得唔錯，叫緊糊叫一萬。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n摸嚟摸去都摸唔撚到，仲要出面一隻一萬都冇，打出嘅冇，上碰都冇。R撚晒頭，又灰灰地。但我又好撚緊張，難得咁耐又冇出沖，又冇人食得出，緊張到一手都係手汗。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n就喺哩個時候，由我摸最後一隻牌!!!!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n到底會唔會畀我海底撈月撈到隻一萬返嚟呢??????<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一摸，一甩，屌你老母真係<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: navy;\">一</span><span style=\"color: red;\">萬</span></span>!!!!!哩隻一萬我等咗你好撚耐! 我終於等到你!!!!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n嗰一下勁撚開心，全身起晒雞皮，準備拎埋自度，插落副牌，好撚型咁開牌大嗌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n各 ● 位 ● 觀 ● 眾<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">十 三 么</span></span><br />\n<br />\n屌你老母我真係好撚緊張好撚多手汗，摸之前我唔撚記得抹抹手先摸，一摸一甩一揭，拎埋自己度嗰時跌咗喺出面。<br />\n<br />\n各位觀眾，你又點會估到<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n噗<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n噗<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n噗<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n三條仆街一齊叫緊一萬。三響炮我屌你咩，我全身又再起多次雞皮。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後，嗰一晚我贏住錢返屋企，仲要贏咗好多。但我一啲都唔開心。<br />\n<br />\n我以後做野會小心啲架喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n十三么你返返嚟我身邊啦嗚嗚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0578748729ce110e6eed4b5bd2e0c58279468e70","tid":1119702,"uid":61005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T06:50:20.000Z","msg":"割禾青"},{"pid":"7648f03eda9405b537d15014ffd38b400f4c5810","tid":1119702,"uid":28149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T06:50:42.000Z","msg":"三家打發財嘅時候，你都要打發財，<br />\n因為咁樣就大家都發財啦"},{"pid":"82320c7ae6f940896f6a7ef98352918795560b62","tid":1119702,"uid":23170,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T06:50:50.000Z","msg":"唔夠真實，閱"},{"pid":"c3222951b99a83a575e7f353c4f0a382d2f57a1c","tid":1119702,"uid":59669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T06:56:18.000Z","msg":"棄糊都唔可以俾機會人"}]}